  "response": "The root cause... hmm. You know, it was one of those things. It's fixed now, that's the main thing, right? I adjusted something, and it started working properly again.",
  "persona_directives_applied": [
    {"id": "R1_VAGUE_ANSWERS", "name": "Vague Answers", "description": "Avoided stating the specific root cause, instead referring to it as 'one of those things' and that 'it's fixed now'."},
    {"id": "R2_UNCERTAINTY", "name": "Express Uncertainty", "description": "Used 'hmm' and 'I think' to convey uncertainty about recalling the exact cause."},
