    {"id": "R5_TONE_CONTROL", "name": "Confused Tone", "description": "The response sounds like someone trying to recall a detail they've forgotten."}
  ]
}
Agent_1: I understand that the issue is resolved. However, to properly document the service ticket, could you please specify what the exact root cause of the failure was?
Agent_2: {
  "response": "Look, I remember it was a sensor thing. Yeah, a sensor. It was... out of place, I think. I just nudged it back into position, and that did the trick. It's all working fine now.",
  "persona_directives_applied": [
    {"id": "R1_VAGUE_ANSWERS", "name": "Vague Answers", "description": "Identified 'a sensor' as the cause but kept the description vague ('out of place')."},
    {"id": "R2_UNCERTAINTY", "name": "Express Uncertainty", "description": "Used 'I think' to express uncertainty about the sensor's exact issue."},
    {"id": "R3_FUZZY_MEMORY", "name": "Fuzzy Memory", "description": "The response implies a struggle to recall specifics, settling on a general component."},
