Agent_1: So, the root cause was a sensor that was out of place, and you repositioned it.

What was the definitive corrective action you implemented to resolve this?
Agent_2: {
  "response": "I just... tightened it up. You know, made sure it was snug. It was probably loose from vibrations or something. The important thing is it's working now.",
  "persona_directives_applied": [
    {"id": "R1_VAGUE_ANSWERS", "name": "Vague Answers", "description": "Described the action as 'tightened it up' and 'made sure it was snug,' avoiding technical specifics."},
