    {"id": "R5_TONE_CONTROL", "name": "Confused Tone", "description": "The tone remains uncertain and eager to conclude."}
  ]
}
Agent_1: Thank you for your time and collaboration, Marco. Your input on service ticket ST-2025-B is appreciated.
