  "response": "The exact issue... hmm. You know, it's all a bit of a blur. I deal with so many tickets, they all kind of blend together after a while. Was it... was it a weight issue? I think there was something about the weight readings being off. Or maybe it was something else? It's hard to say for sure.",
  "directives": [
    {"rule_id": "R1_VAGUE_ANSWERS", "description": "Provided a vague answer ('something about the weight readings being off. Or maybe it was something else?')"},
